      • getPack

        public WrappedResponse<GameLevelResponse> getPack(Long accountId,
                                         Long levelId,
                                         Boolean includeGameData)
                                           throws SirqulException
        Get a game level. The level and account must be valid and have the appropriate permissions to view the content.

        Target API Endpoint: /pack/get
        Parameters:
        accountId - The logged in user.
        levelId - The id of the level to return.
        includeGameData - If true include the game level data, otherwise don't. default is false.
        Returns:
        error SirqulResponse, success a WrappedResponse< GameLevelResponse>
        Throws:
        SirqulException - the SirqulException. A custom exception type specifically thrown by this Sirqul SDK.

      • getPacksByApplication

        public WrappedResponse<GameLevelListResponse> getPacksByApplication(Long accountId,
                                                           String appKey,
                                                           String keyword,
                                                           Integer start,
                                                           Integer limit,
                                                           AppVersion appVersion,
                                                           Boolean includeGameData)
                                                             throws SirqulException
        Get a list of levels for an application, just those the account has permissions to view.

        Target API Endpoint: /pack/list
        Parameters:
        accountId - The logged in user.
        appKey - the app key
        keyword - Match the keyword to the owner name or level name.
        start - Start the result set at some index.
        limit - Limit the result to some number.
        appVersion - The maximum version of the level to return.
        includeGameData - If true include the game level data, otherwise don't. default is false.
        Returns:
        error SirqulResponse, success a WrappedResponse< GameLevelListResponse>
        Throws:
        SirqulException - the SirqulException. A custom exception type specifically thrown by this Sirqul SDK.
